1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Welcome to LuminFlow.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:06,000
An AI-powered audit transparency platform,
built on the COSO 2013 framework.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:11,000
The Dashboard delivers real-time visibility
into audit progress and control coverage.

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:15,000
Track PBC completion and aggregated risk
scores across the engagement.

5
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Role-based views adapt instantly for
Auditors, Partners, and CFOs.

6
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:25,000
A live heatmap, stepper, and activity
timeline keep every stakeholder aligned.

7
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:30,000
TraceMap visualizes the COSO 2013
three-level objective hierarchy.

8
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:34,000
An interactive audit tree connects
objectives, risks, and controls.

9
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:39,000
AI Insight decomposes strategic goals
into testable, traceable controls.

10
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:43,000
A radar chart benchmarks coverage
across multiple audit dimensions.

11
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:48,000
HeatLens unifies the full risk landscape
with the Risk Control Matrix.

12
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:53,000
Tune weights for inherent risk and
control effectiveness in real time.

13
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:58,000
Multi-factor scoring captures the true
residual exposure no single metric can.

14
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:03,000
SampleLens recommends optimal sample
sizes through AI-driven analysis.

15
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:07,000
Supports monetary unit and attribute
sampling methodologies.

16
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:12,000
Tune confidence, tolerable, and expected
deviation rates with full transparency.

17
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:16,000
Event-driven reinforcement expands
samples when control risk rises.

18
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:21,000
PBCView centralizes Provided-By-Client
document management end to end.

19
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:25,000
AI auto-generates tailored PBC lists
by industry and audit process.

20
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:29,000
Overdue alerts and reminder emails
accelerate every client response.

21
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:33,000
Progress tracked by control area
streamlines auditor-client exchange.

22
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:38,000
NarrativeLens turns raw findings into
structured narratives via generative AI.

23
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:42,000
Key points are extracted automatically
and prepared for review.

24
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:46,000
A three-step flow routes drafts through
Submit, Manager, and Partner sign-off.

25
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:50,000
Human-AI collaboration safeguards
every narrative's audit quality.

26
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:55,000
ImpactSimulator models the outcome
of any control deficiency.

27
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:59,000
A force-directed graph traces how risk
propagates through connected nodes.

28
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:04,000
Quantify potential financial loss
and regulatory penalty exposure.

29
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:08,000
AI ranks remediation priority
by projected business impact.

30
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:13,000
TeamPanel governs a multi-role
permission matrix for the engagement.

31
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:17,000
From Audit Manager to Client Liaison,
visibility is scoped per dataset.

32
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:21,000
The AI assistant answers natural-language
audit queries instantly.

33
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:25,000
Analyze risks, generate sampling plans,
or explain COSO principles on demand.

34
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:28,000
API data integrations are managed
from one unified console.

35
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:33,000
Every module connects into one
continuous, end-to-end workflow.

36
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:37,000
Data flows across planning, execution,
and assessment without friction.

37
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:42,000
RESTful APIs open LuminFlow to ERP,
GRC, and external audit systems.

38
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:47,000
From planning to sign-off, LuminFlow
unifies every audit signal.

39
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:51,000
Faster cycles, sharper insight,
and defensible evidence at every step.

40
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:55,000
Audit transparency, redefined.

41
00:02:55,000 --> 00:03:00,000
Step into LuminFlow and discover
intelligent assurance in action.
